    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They have these nocturnal whatever stimulations and so-- but even so, we did not succeed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But to some extent, it had the scars, which would indicate that this person maybe was not circumcised but underwent some operations due to some venereal disease or so forth.",
